longBusinessSummary: Prisma Properties AB (publ) owns, develops, and leases properties in Sweden, Denmark, and Norway. It owns and develops properties within the discount retail, grocery, and fast-food sectors. The company was founded in 2016 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
